    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! You are seriously going to love this ride. It\u2019s in absolutely stunning condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, keeping it spotless and making sure it runs like a dream. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s basically brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 46500.0,
