      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a superlative E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54B32 power unit equipped with individual throttle bodies and a fully serviced double-VANOS system. This example boasts a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox with short-throw precision, delivering torque to a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis integrity is paramount; the rear subframe has been reinforced, and the rod bearings have been addressed with high-performance coated shells for long-term reliability. Every suspension component maintains factory tolerances, ensuring razor-sharp turn-in and communicative feedback. The exterior retains its original finish with uniform depth, while the interior remains free of wear or electronic gremlins. A mechanically impeccable, turn-key investment for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
