    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously garaged and pampered, boasting a flawless exterior with a deep, mirror-like finish and absolutely zero imperfections. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium leather remains supple and scent-free, with every electronic component and dial functioning perfectly. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, supported by a comprehensive folder of service records from day one. With remarkably low mileage and a smooth, whisper-quiet ride, this is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example. No scratches, no stories\u2014just pure automotive excellence for the discerning buyer.",
      "price": 46500.0,
